Economic efficiency check
In the case of a sample in a superstructure management, the most favourable tenders for three quarters of the award procedures examined decreased more than 10% from the estimated costs previously determined.
Every twentieth award procedure has been cancelled due to inappropriate tender prices.
Not all bidding tests and reconnaissance talks with bidders were comprehensible or sufficiently documented.
There was often a lack of further reconnaissance, such as at the unit prices of the main positions.
The deviations were often justified only on a flat-rate basis, e.g. For example, by indicating changes in market prices or increased material costs.
Construction departments stated that detecting and proving compound calculations was difficult.
In the case of an invitation to tender by an institution of public law, the tender price of the most favourable tender was 66% lower than the previously established estimate value of those services.
Further calculation tests or studies on the causes of this deviation were not documented.
In a reconnaissance meeting, the awarding agency did not find any evidence of price dumping by the company then commissioned.
This left it unclear whether the estimated estimate value increased or the offer price was too low.
Later, the contracting entity assessed the commissioned company as a "low-cost company," which could not hold quality or deadlines.
In the case of another invitation to tender, a construction service awarded the tender to a tender the price of which was 35% higher than the value of the cost assessment.
It did not lift the invitation to tender, arguing that the company could be closed to a foreign calculation.
Suspicion of irregularities
There were two cases of irregularities in an audit of construction management, both of which were reported to the expert supervisor.
In one of the cases, in the case of an invitation to tender, the calculation of two tenderers was identical, so the contracting authority excluded both tenders from the procedure.
In the application of the other rules, the tests did not produce any material complaints.
